# Git LFS tracking removed — see issue #26.
#
# Git LFS is disabled for this repository, so the LFS filter rules that
# were here caused clone/checkout failures:
#
#   error: external filter 'git-lfs filter-process' failed
#   fatal: smudge filter lfs failed
#
# All files previously tracked by LFS were already committed as full-size
# objects (not pointer stubs), so removing the filter rules is safe and
# allows the repository to clone and check out normally without LFS.
